large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 39244, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281", "stars": 5458, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 628726, "username": "naminokoe", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/naminokoe", "website": "https://springwood.me", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_mini.png?m=1683930048", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_normal.png?m=1683930048", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_large.png?m=1683930048", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_xlarge.png?m=1683930048", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_xlarge.png?m=1683930048", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a01d/3a9c/628726_xlarge.png?m=1683930048", "created": 1683929846, "last_modified": 1683930048}, "last_reply_by": "LokiSharp", "last_touched": 1691899279, "title": "最近整理了一下古籍，发现很多我们背的著名的古诗词和原著都不太一样", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/964852", "created": 1691899347, "deleted": 0, "content": "比如李白的《静夜思》原著是：\r\n\r\n```\r\n床前看月光，\r\n疑是地上霜。\r\n举头望山月，\r\n低头思故乡。\r\n```\r\n第一句和第三句与我们背的都不一样。\r\n\r\n我一共整理了 16 首著名的古诗词，[详见此处]( https://springwood.me/poem-different-version/)。\r\n\r\n另外还发现很多李鬼，《夜宿山寺》不是李白写的，《画》不是王维写的，《清明》也不是杜牧写的，以后教小孩背诗可得注意一点。", "content_rendered": "<p>比如李白的《静夜思》原著是：</p>\n<pre><code>床前看月光，\n疑是地上霜。\n举头望山月，\n低头思故乡。\n</code></pre>\n<p>第一句和第三句与我们背的都不一样。</p>\n<p>我一共整理了 16 首著名的古诗词，<a href=\"https://springwood.me/poem-different-version/\" rel=\"nofollow\">详见此处</a>。</p>\n<p>另外还发现很多李鬼，《夜宿山寺》不是李白写的，《画》不是王维写的，《清明》也不是杜牧写的，以后教小孩背诗可得注意一点。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1691899347, "replies": 89, "id": 964852}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9c3b/1830/1113_large.png?m=1652442934", "name": "crypto", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9c3b/1830/1113_normal.png?m=1652442934", "title": "加密货币", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/crypto", "topics": 72, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Crypto", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9c3b/1830/1113_mini.png?m=1652442934", "stars": 273, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1113, "parent_node_name": "blockchain"}, "member": {"id": 250937, "username": "ttentau1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ttentau1", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0783/d631/250937_mini.png?m=1687831594", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0783/d631/250937_normal.png?m=1687831594", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0783/d631/250937_large.png?m=1687831594", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0783/d631/250937_xlarge.png?m=1687831594", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0783/d631/250937_xlarge.png?m=1687831594", "created": 1503739462, "last_modified": 1687831594}, "last_reply_by": "Tezos", "last_touched": 1691980756, "title": "币安的 USDT 保本理财稳吗？年化能有 4%", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/964845", "created": 1691897605, "deleted": 0, "content": "如下图，昨天买了 1000$\r\n\r\n![img]( https://i.imgur.com/n1NP2jE.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p>如下图，昨天买了 1000$</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/n1NP2jE.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1691921414, "replies": 83, "id": 964845}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4